Scorponok

Scorponok walked back to the Predacons base. The whole time he was 
messing woth the mindwhipping device that Megatron never took. "Hmmm, 
I like the feel to this one, Guess that I'm going to have to destroy 
the other one."

Scorponok gets to the Predacon ship. He walks to his run and hears 
blaster fire. He runs in and sees Hell Beast and other Predacon
firing 
at something near the roof. He looked up to see this weird looking 
bot. He wasn't Oragainc nor TM1 nor TM2. Scorponok slowly crept into 
his room. He walked behind everyone so he wouldn't be noticed.
